it.unitn.disi.ds2.whanau.controls

Class WhanauSetup

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unitn.disi.ds2.whanau.controls.WhanauSetup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    peersim.core.Control
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    WhanauLookup

    public class WhanauSetup
extends java.lang.Object
implements peersim.core.Control
    Control class which implements the logic of the setup() method presented in the Whanau's paper. This class enables us to build the internal tables of each nodes.
